PLUS-SIZE Nollywood actress and producer, Eniola Badmus, is set to launch a television channel, Eniola Badmus TV. Eniola, who just released a movie titled, ‘Madam Cash’, said that the new TV channel would have different segments that will be filled with entertainments. “Eniola Badmus TV coming up with different segments… kindly click link in my bio to subscribe to my YouTube channel and get notification once new video drops… entertainment without bounds,” she wrote. The segments include – lifestyle, movie, fashion, music, touring, events, among others.